songs.title: My thoughts are really bad for you (runaway from me) log #1.5
songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1: XXXTENTACION]
(a radio box picks a signal)
(transmission begins)
My thoughts with demons up on the ceiling
tellin me what i should be feelin
I'm trapped in my own damn thoughts
whenever i try to leave it never worked like always
Feeling like im livin in a damn cot
whenever i fall all the demons tell me "you're parents are always told me you're a fuck up"
Whenever my demons remind me of that i just think to myself what the fuck am i feeling???

[Verse 2: XXXTENTACION]
My thoughts are always bad whenever i picture me doing something important to my parents
They never believed in me
What did i think? Of them or me?
Of course no one
You never prescribed my life as a real job
You've tormented me
You've tormented me (yaaaaaaahh)
You've tormented me
And now you'll pay, you sick fu--
(transmission ends)

(transmission picks up weakly)
Welcome to my thoughts
My thoughts are really bad for you aren't they kiddo?
Runaway... dont fucking come back unless you want to dive deep int the rabbit hole I call my mind you little shit!
